function.name: GetEntity1

function.name: GetEntity2
function.desc: Returns the second entity involved in the contact.

function.name: GetCollisionObject1
function.desc: Returns the collision object of the first entity involved in the contact.

function.name: GetCollisionObject2
function.desc: Returns the collision object of the second entity involved in the contact.

function.name: GetPhysicsObject1
function.desc: Returns the physics object of the first entity involved in the contact.

function.name: GetPhysicsObject2
function.desc: Returns the physics object of the second entity involved in the contact.

function.name: GetContactPos1
function.desc: Returns the contact position of the first entity involved in the contact.

function.name: GetContactPos2
function.desc: Returns the contact position of the second entity involved in the contact.

function.name: GetHitNormal
function.desc: Returns the hit normal of the contact.
